title: The Beatles - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 12/8/20

description:
George Noory and music historian Chuck Gunderson discuss his work chronicling the Beatles popularity on tour following their iconic appearance on the Ed Sullivan TV show, and mark the 40th anniversary of the murder of John Lennon.
